Package org.cesecore.certificates.endentity

Class ExtendedInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cesecore.internal.UpgradeableDataHashMap
      • org.cesecore.certificates.endentity.ExtendedInformation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IUpgradeableData
    public class ExtendedInformation
extends UpgradeableDataHashMap
implements Serializable
    The model representation of Extended Information about a user. It's used for non-searchable data about a user, like a image, in an effort to minimize the need for database alterations TODO: Clean out whatever final static variables which aren't externally references.
    Version:
    $Id: ExtendedInformation.java 34306 2020-01-16 12:21:31Z andrey_s_helmes $
